# =============================================================================
# Metamates  monorepo — 根目录 .gitignore
# 开源主体：metamates-app/  详见 metamates-app/docs/OPEN_SOURCE.md
# =============================================================================

# --- 个人 Vault / 测试数据（绝不开源）---
MyMetaMates/
Test/
MyM2/

# --- 参考副本 / 历史备份（非本仓库源码）---
AionUi-source/
terminal-test/
metamates-opensource/
metamates-opensource-backup-*/
backup/

# --- 内部备忘（含本地路径、迭代笔记，不随开源发布）---
PLAN.md
VERSION.md
project_rules.md
功能确认.md
错误记录.md
clean-repo.cmd

# --- 大型或非代码附件 ---
*.pdf

# --- 临时 UI 草稿（根目录）---
hello.html
theme-*.html

# --- 图片：默认忽略，保留产品资源 ---
*.png
!metamates-app/logo.png
!metamates-app/build/icon.png
!metamates-app/public/**/*.png
!metamates-app/src/**/*.png

*.jpg
*.jpeg
!metamates-app/public/**/*
!metamates-app/src/**/*

# --- Obsidian / 本地 PDF 等（若出现在根目录）---
Obsidian + Claude Codebook (doc).pdf

# --- Cursor IDE 本地规则（机器相关，不随开源发布）---
.cursor/

# --- 用户数据 / 密钥（若误放在仓库根目录）---
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local
conversations.db
conversations.db.bak
conversations.sqlite
conversations.sqlite-wal
conversations.sqlite-shm
session-store.json
*.pfx
*.p12
